snippet.title: Warner Bros. fears Depp allegations could impact Harry Potter spin-off series
snippet.description:
VideoImage
Johnny Depp suing ex-wife Amber Heard for $70million 0:27
Actor Johnny Depp is taking legal action against his ex-wife Amber Heard accusing her of defamation. An article in the Washington Post, written by Heard, detailed the backlash she faced after speaking out about domestic violence. Mr Depp's lawsuit says he 'never abused Ms Heard' and says the claims are 'part of an elaborate hoax' to advance her career. He is seeking more than $70 million in damages. 
March 3rd 2019a month ago/display/newscorpaustralia.com/Web/NewsNetwork/Entertainment - syndicated/
Amber Heard and Johnny Depp in 2014. Picture: Getty ImagesSource:Getty Images 
Warner Bros. is reportedly “freaking out” over its hit Harry Potter movie franchise’s connection to Johnny Depp.
